request.description:
### Get Organization Source Tracking Codes

This endpoint retrieves the source tracking codes for an organization, with options to include source tracking codes for fundraising teams, fundraising pages, and transactions.

#### Response

The response is a JSON object with the following schema. For the most up to date version of this, please visit [docs.classy.org](https://docs.classy.org)

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "error": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "permissions": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "action": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "entity": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "queries_log": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "query": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "bindings": {
                        "type": "array",
                        "items": {
                            "type": "string"
                        }
                    },
                    "time": {
                        "type": "number"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "scopes": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "organization": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "number"
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

